<font color=red>
<h1>Software Architecture</h1>

<h2>Software architecture is the arrangement of its components
into one or more structures defined by
the functional role played by each component
and the interaction relationships exhibited
by the components.</h2>
</font>
<h2>Key elements: components, connections and behaviors</h2>

